he says, hopefully.

55:11.381 --> 55:14.321
I'm thinking about George Hathaway,
to tell you the truth.

55:14.425 --> 55:15.706
Who's that?

55:16.386 --> 55:20.004
He's the reporter who wrote that piece
in <i>Inside Sports</i> magazine.

55:20.557 --> 55:22.430
What made you think of him?

55:24.519 --> 55:26.844
I think about the press a lot nowadays.

55:28.690 --> 55:30.232
Anything specific?

55:32.569 --> 55:36.103
I was wondering if he has any idea
what his article did to all of us?

55:38.158 --> 55:39.865
What do you mean, exactly?

55:42.287 --> 55:44.991
It's very hard for me
to trust anybody, anymore.

55:46.124 --> 55:47.618
On any level.

55:50.545 --> 55:52.651
My mom and I didn't talk for a year.

55:52.755 --> 55:55.709
See, she was the one who gave him
most of his information.

55:56.050 --> 55:58.838
Although, she says she didn't say
what he printed.

56:00.471 --> 56:02.963
It didn't matter
because my coach lost his job.

56:04.684 --> 56:06.593
His wife left him, took their kids.

56:07.187 --> 56:11.462
