59:40.525 --> 59:42.731
Adam, eat shit and die.

59:47.574 --> 59:49.234
We want Boy!

59:52.370 --> 59:54.727
- Yes, Mark?
- Then some guy calls and says...

59:54.831 --> 59:58.116
no health club will keep you healthy
if McKenzie's story runs.

59:58.418 --> 01:00:02.234
