01:02:14.971 --> 01:02:18.162
- How long has he been doing this?
- Ever since she met him.

01:02:18.266 --> 01:02:22.333
- They met at the Sports Connection, right?
- Right. The first day we joined.

01:02:22.437 --> 01:02:24.626
- She's so lucky.
- Yeah.

01:02:24.731 --> 01:02:27.138
She had no idea he was a male stripper.

01:02:38.912 --> 01:02:40.785
That's my lover who's out there.

01:02:53.343 --> 01:02:55.783
<i>Ladies in the back,
