01:04:48.750 --> 01:04:49.855
He's real nice.

01:04:49.959 --> 01:04:53.400
- He's been on <i>Merv Griffin.</i>
- You know, it doesn't surprise me.

01:04:53.505 --> 01:04:55.778
- What?
