01:05:08.895 --> 01:05:11.351
I'll be right back.
I have to talk to Sally.

01:05:14.400 --> 01:05:16.974
Sally. Sally, come here.

01:05:17.821 --> 01:05:20.177
- It's going great, isn't it?
- Fantastic.

01:05:20.281 --> 01:05:23.485
Listen, he is so charming.
